            "body": "I got that error when I used the cpanminus package from Debian.\r\n\r\nWhen I installed cpanminus using cpan, the error went away.\r\n\r\nI suppose that the recommended install method would also work:\r\n\r\n```\r\ncurl -L https://cpanmin.us | sudo perl - App::cpanminus\r\n```\r\n\r\nSee here: https://metacpan.org/pod/App::cpanminus",
